{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d89c850de","title":"最后通牒","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"05462c5b90","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"5d89c850de","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"破四旧","id":"9ec766296f","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b6c96579d7","name":"红旗路大街111号(即交中)红卫兵"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5593330aac","type":"title","text":"最后通牒","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab55042574","type":"paragraph","text":"最后通牒","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9854c40e4a","type":"paragraph","text":"红旗路大街111号（即交中）红卫兵","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e46a20d17d","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.08.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b10aa5cd7f","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的形势正以雷霆万钧之力，排山倒海之势猛烈地冲击着旧的习惯，旧的思想，旧的文化，旧的风俗。打得那些资产阶级的老爷们、资产阶级的狗崽子们无法藏身，狼狈不堪。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ee36d5448","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是旧世界的造反者。我们就是要造资产阶级的反，造旧制度的反，造一切不符合革命的一切事物的反。造反，造反，造反精神万岁！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54e895e2e1","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，我们采取了一系列的措施──在大街上造反。有些资产阶级的老爷们，封建的老爷们，狗崽子们，还是极力保护，虽然他们表面上勉强同意我们造反，实际他们怀恨在心，有的流氓，资产阶级，旧制度，旧世界的辩护士们在暗中搞破坏造谣言……等等诸如此类的事情……","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcf1565a54","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不客气地发出最后通牒：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d01272f496","type":"paragraph","text":"一、一切非国营企业，立即筹备交给国家管理。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ca91b5d33","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在十一之前各路牌工作组等负责单位，把北京所有封建的，资产阶级的，反动的，一切不是革命的路牌立即更换，换上革命的路牌。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6eeb7082cb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、在商店、企业、社会上一切不健康的东西，群众为不拥护的东西，在十一以前都要收回，否则后果你们要负完全责任。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15159687b6","type":"paragraph","text":"四、在十一以前，把鸽子一律卖给国家和自己处理，不要养鸽子，因为这是一种旧的坏的习气。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a80ccf2398","type":"paragraph","text":"五、不许一切流氓，小贩在街上卖鸟卖蟋蟀，卖蝉。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49a52e8792","type":"paragraph","text":"六、警告那些流氓，如果你们再不老实，我们红卫兵对你们不客气。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3188f60bf2","type":"paragraph","text":"正告那些资产阶级的老爷们，资产阶级的狗崽子们，混蛋们，你们老实点！我们用毛泽东思想武装起来的红卫兵、革命小将就是勇敢，就是    （编者注：此处有两个字不清楚），在你们看来就是可怕！我们要打你们，不让你们这些臭思想，臭习气，臭东西在我们伟大的国家里逗留片刻。我们要誓死捍卫我们革 命先烈用血换来的江山，誓死保卫党中央，誓死保卫毛主席，誓死保卫无产阶级专政，为革命事业，而献出我们一切力量。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aab50478aa","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的造反精神万岁！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b6214d52d","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党万岁！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"555ccdcd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们最伟大的领袖、导师、舵手毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cf515f31e","type":"paragraph","text":"红旗路大街111号（即交中）红卫兵","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"912d482d39","type":"paragraph","text":"（原件为传单，成文时间不清楚，应在１９６６年８月下旬──编者注）","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d89c850de","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}